SKU Serial: 2261153

Description:

Clean lines, a beautiful weathered natural finish, with led light feature create a chic bedroom retreat with the Palm Grove collection. The panel bed, with crisp, straight lines, is sure to fit in all room settings. Coordinating items such as the dresser, chest and nightstand features LED nightlights that allow you to see in the drawers when all the lights are off. The hardware is finished in a brushed nickel finish.

$149.99

Features:

Extra Durable Melanie laminate

Select Hard Woods

*dresser sold seperately
